### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Create interview
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/interviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target_role": "后端开发",
  "level": "校招",
  "round_type": "项目面"
}

### Reply
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/interviews/{{interview_id}}/reply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "answer": "我做过一个高并发活动系统，负责缓存、异步队列和接口性能优化。"
}

### Finish
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/interviews/{{interview_id}}/finish
